Other in-game reasons for baddies to kill fallen foes include

* Death Knell spell gives you a positive benefit for killing him
* Vampiric Touch, though you won't get much benefit.
* Chop the head off and brandish it at the opponents for a
circumstance bonus to Intimidate
* Animate Dead
* Threatening to kill a PC allows a BBEG to escape. This is easiest if
the PC is portable (a halfling, gnome, etc)
* Souls for my lord Arioch
* Food
* If some monsters can't get at the rest of the PCs, they'll kill and
loot the body for something to do, and to get the loot before someone
else does.

